re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"係嗌比講獨撚聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f258b52b80edb7de2d51297fe36bfd7066310b7d","tid":2031314,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得「只有兩國，才有兩制」呢句好中 我一直覺得港獨未係時候 但呢句真係好適合今次主題"},{"pid":"19ccf74093e3fdf2dc908c4b5e092987cd73e8d8","tid":2031314,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"見到標題已經入嚟比正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族性從來要建立係自己嘅心入面<br />\n冇「民族」嘅肯定 又何來有「自強」嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n你睇下台灣 國家有難 台灣人唔會諗移民 離開<br />\n因為佢地對自己土生土長嘅地方有一體嘅覺悟<br />\n反觀香港......<br />\n<br />\n民族自強 自己對香港都冇民族性 仲學咩人講本土？"},{"pid":"032b2d3ab4642b10a6aca8434b0bce8c02bae29f","tid":2031314,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f258b52b80edb7de2d51297fe36bfd7066310b7d","tid":2031314,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得「只有兩國，才有兩制」呢句好中 我一直覺得港獨未係時候 但呢句真係好適合今次主題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:57:44.000Z","msg":"要睇係唔係時候，嗌出黎就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正之後嗌乜野都會比人拉"},{"pid":"11356374fa3e70feb5aeab82792daf8f0432ef0a","tid":2031314,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555d11bf3a8b05066a2b8ef3d90f15b36bca1536","tid":2031314,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c326f730dbd072e41008d5f338af843bda7bcae","tid":2031314,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae5009c6934366e9daec051bc68515088d148104","tid":2031314,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"唔好支持我，支持香港人<br />\n相信香港民族"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"支持你篇文唔好沉底啫<b